---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="How PleasureWatch works">
  <main class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1>How PleasureWatch works</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">Alex Mercer writes with clear, non-judgmental language. We keep practical tips separated from anything that should come from a clinician.</p>


    <h2>Sources & updates</h2>
    <p>We keep shopping fields current where possible, note time ranges on charts, and flag when data is limited.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
